Package org.universAAL.kinect.adapter.contextBus

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    AbstractContext
    This interface links non universAAL object to universAAL specific ContextEvents thus acts as an adapter.
    IContextCallback
    This is a callback interface for ContextEvents.
    IContextPublisher
    This is an interface for publishing ContextEvents.
